Derivative of Velocity Distribution of Species is:
  -subroutine: derivative_f0 (ALPS_fns.f90)
  -file: distribution/'arrayName'_dfdv.'is'.array
  -data: pp(is,iperp,ipar,1:2),df0(is, iperp,ipar,1:2)
	
The Velocity Distribution itself is found in:
  -subroutine: generated by 'generate_distribution.f90'
  -file: distribution/'arrayName'.'is'.array
  -data: pp(is,iperp,ipar,1:2),f(is, iperp,ipar,1:2)

The Bessel Function Array for processor ip
  -subroutine: determine_bessel_array (ALPS_fns.f90)
  -file: solution/besselArray.ip.out
  -data: nn, iperp, z, bessel_array(nn,iperp)

The Map (grid in omega,gamma) of Dispersion Solutions
  -subroutine: map_search (ALPS_fns.f90)
  -file: solution/'runname'.map
  -data: ir,ii,om(ir,ii),log10(val(ir,ii)),cal(ir,ii)

The Listing of Roots
  -subroutine: refine_guess (ALPS_fns.f90)
  -file: solution/'runname'.roots
  -data: iw,wroots(iw),log10(abs(tmpDisp)),tmpDisp